Package: jugglr
Title: Juggling Pattern Validation and Visualisation
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Ella", "Kaye", , "ella.kaye@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: Validate and visualise juggling patterns expressed in siteswap
    notation. Supports vanilla and synchronous siteswap, with tools to check
    pattern validity, produce timeline arc diagrams and ladder diagrams, retrieve
    raw throw data for custom visualisations, and animate patterns via the
    JugglingLab GIF server.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
